---
title: Duck Breast with Mustard Lentils and Garlicky Cabbage
description: We love good Duck Breast with Mustard Lentils and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/duck-breast-with-mustard-lentils-454bde92-c29651e1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/duck-breast-with-mustard-lentils-5da9b8e340ee583b4c03e518-5d22a920.pdf
